               <p>JOHN DRINKWATER. I was coming, on the 1st of August, from <placeName id="t18310908-313-crimeloc1613">Hanwell</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-313-crimeloc1613" type="placeName" value="Hanwell"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-313-crimeloc1613" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-313-off1611 t18310908-313-crimeloc1613"></join> to <placeName id="t18310908-313-crimeloc1614">Brompton</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-313-crimeloc1614" type="placeName" value="Brompton"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18310908-313-crimeloc1614" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-313-off1611 t18310908-313-crimeloc1614"></join>; my mother and brother were with me - I was taken unwell, and retired; I fell into a fit, and as I was recovering, I found the prisoner's right hand in my right-hand waistcoat pocket, where I had a box, containing two duplicates - he still staid with me; we then went on; I told my brother and mother of it, but I did not ask the prisoner for the box - we went on to the Seven Stars, and called for a pint of beer; the prisoner followed us in - I sent for the Policeman; my brother knew the prisoner, but I did not.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-313-person2259">
                  WILLIAM 
                  PEASGOOD
               <interp inst="t18310908-313-person2259" type="surname" value="PEASGOOD"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-313-person2259" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-313-person2259" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a Policeman. I took the prisoner; I said, "I want you, you know what for;" he said, "I shan't come;" the prosecutor then said, "I give him in charge;" the prisoner said, "Oh! about this box," and took it out of his pocket - I said, "Give it to me;" he said, "I shan't," and put it into his pocket again - I took him to the station.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310908-313-person2260">
                  THOMAS 
                  DRINKWATER
               <interp inst="t18310908-313-person2260" type="surname" value="DRINKWATER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-313-person2260" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310908-313-person2260" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with my brother - I did not see the prisoner take the box, but I saw him pull it out at the public-house.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He said would I give up the box; I said not till I got to the office.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18310908-313-verdict1615" type="verdictDescription">
